Steps I Followed:

1️⃣ First, create the structure of the table in SQL.

2️⃣ Go to the database schemas section and select the required table.

3️⃣ Right-click on the table.

4️⃣ Select **Import/Export Data**.

5️⃣ A dialog box will open.

6️⃣ Click the **Import** option.

7️⃣ Select the CSV file from your system.

8️⃣ Choose the file format as **CSV**.

9️⃣ Click **Next/Finish** to complete the import process.

🔟 Finally, open the table to verify that the data has been imported successfully.
